{"tid":1446237,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有無法律朋友可以解答下卧底示威者問題","createTime":"2019-08-11T14:50:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T09:52:35.000Z","uid":296826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"be73984408ef8b91b7fa363299033c77331648a1","tid":1446237,"uid":296826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:50:03.000Z","msg":"據我所知卧底都要向律政司申請豁免刑事起訴，因為卧底行動可能涉及違法行為.<br />\n如果無佢地有可能涉及暴動罪.更唔可以告捉左的義士.<br />\n我想問我有無理解錯?定係無法無天到唔洗?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dc310f43cc0e43375b6bf01dfc3d4b51058af48","tid":1446237,"uid":296826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"be73984408ef8b91b7fa363299033c77331648a1","tid":1446237,"uid":296826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:50:03.000Z","msg":"據我所知卧底都要向律政司申請豁免刑事起訴，因為卧底行動可能涉及違法行為.<br />\n如果無佢地有可能涉及暴動罪.更唔可以告捉左的義士.<br />\n我想問我有無理解錯?定係無法無天到唔洗?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:51:43.000Z","msg":"有無人知<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05e0e13f4741a56cb56be2d4b97e5c0a3c3f1386","tid":1446237,"uid":296826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:57:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"35579bab47304b9bf011798ea6564b9bde565d96","tid":1446237,"uid":296826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:58:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b7eae1eb687bcb5863240726d67536f1bbfc1b7f","tid":1446237,"uid":109689,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:58:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://endlesslawstudy.blogspot.com/2014/07/secretary-of-justice-v-lam-tat-ming.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fendlesslawstudy.blogspot.com%2F2014%2F07%2Fsecretary-of-justice-v-lam-tat-ming.html&d=rP1lJsqA2sO3Td0%2BA1LJ516E%2F45TZQXVIGc6puLiPLc%3D&h=243ffb87\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://endlesslawstudy.blogspot.com/2014/07/secretary-of-justice-v-lam-tat-ming.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">如果臥底人員只是扮演了<strong>被動</strong>的角色，聽到或者偷聽到被告的供認，或者保存了該供認，那麼沒有理由拒絕這類的證據。（本案判決書第38段）<br />\n<br />\n如果臥底人員扮演了<strong>主動</strong>的角色，向犯罪嫌疑人提問，誘導了其供認，法庭就需要考慮是否行使酌情權將該份供認排除在外。（本案判決書第39段）</span>"},{"pid":"81e85f98020fa51a21a3a74c16c79c1f607f1877","tid":1446237,"uid":296826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:58:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3c72f40198b44b0214353c9bbceb0a02c5253dc1","tid":1446237,"uid":109689,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:14:52.000Z","msg":"簡單D講，案例係對義士不利的。<br />\n<br />\n大部份時間法庭係唔理會證據係由咩手段獲得，即使係POPO 使用非法手段取得。只係係極為過份既時候，法庭先會介入排除一D &quot;非法證據&quot;。<br />\n<br />\n即使有臥底做左非法行為，而義士又跟住做，呢個唔會係抗辯理由。法庭既睇法係人係有自由意志，能夠判斷咩係啱，咩係錯。"},{"pid":"260a2b90043084eb919dc2ecb72724fbfced7038","tid":1446237,"uid":296826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:52:35.000Z","msg":"佢地真係分分鐘自己犯法"}]}